org.alljoyn.ioe.controlpanelservice.ui

Class ErrorWidget

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.alljoyn.ioe.controlpanelservice.ui.UIElement
      • org.alljoyn.ioe.controlpanelservice.ui.ErrorWidget

  • public class ErrorWidget
extends UIElement
    The widget is used to replace a UIElement that had a failure in its creation
    Use the getLabel() method to receive a proposed label for this widget.
    Use the getError() method to receive an error description that triggered creation of this widget
